    <title>vscode配置c语言环境</title>
    <link href="/2024/06/vscode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEc%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/"/>
    <url>/2024/06/vscode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEc%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="vscode-c语言"><a href="#vscode-c语言" class="headerlink" title="vscode_c语言"></a>vscode_c语言</h1><h2 id="前置："><a href="#前置：" class="headerlink" title="前置："></a>前置：</h2><p>下载vscode后，可选择是否安装中文插件</p><p>下载mingw64，并且配置环境变量Path</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803966.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 093906"></p><h2 id="c文件配置"><a href="#c文件配置" class="headerlink" title="c文件配置"></a>c文件配置</h2><h3 id="设置编译选项"><a href="#设置编译选项" class="headerlink" title="设置编译选项"></a>设置编译选项</h3><p>ctrl+shift+p后选择c&#x2F;c++编辑配置(UI)</p><p>此处选择自己的gcc路径</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803967.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 094658"></p><p>第二处更改</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803968.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 172018"></p><h3 id="生成tasks-json文件"><a href="#生成tasks-json文件" class="headerlink" title="生成tasks.json文件"></a>生成tasks.json文件</h3><p>打开终端，配置任务，选择c&#x2F;c++：gcc.exe生成活动文件tasks.json，修改一些参数</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;version&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2.0.0&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;tasks&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;cppbuild&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;label&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;C/C++: gcc.exe 生成活动文件&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;D:\\vscode\\mingw64\\bin\\gcc.exe&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-comment">//修改你的gcc.exe文件的路径</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;args&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-fdiagnostics-color=always&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-g&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;file&#125;&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-o&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;fileDirname&#125;\\$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span><span class="hljs-comment">//此处为生成文件的文件名</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;options&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;fileDirname&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;problemMatcher&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$gcc&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;group&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;build&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;detail&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;编译器: D:\\vscode\\mingw64\\bin\\gcc.exe&quot;</span><span class="hljs-comment">//修改你的gcc.exe文件的路径</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="运行文件"><a href="#运行文件" class="headerlink" title="运行文件"></a>运行文件</h3><p>打开终端，运行生成任务，选择你的gcc文件，生成.exe文件</p><p>ctrl+&#96;运行，输入.&#x2F;1.exe（即刚生成的exe文件）</p><h3 id="项目型文件的环境配置"><a href="#项目型文件的环境配置" class="headerlink" title="项目型文件的环境配置"></a>项目型文件的环境配置</h3><p>主要是修改tasks.json文件</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803969.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 161238"></p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;version&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2.0.0&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;tasks&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;cppbuild&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;label&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;C/C++: gcc.exe 生成活动文件&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;D:/vscode/mingw64/bin/gcc.exe&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;args&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-fdiagnostics-color=always&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-g&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;\\*.C&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-o&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;\\$&#123;workspaceRootFolderName&#125;.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;options&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;D:/vscode/mingw64/bin&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;problemMatcher&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$gcc&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;group&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;build&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;detail&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;编译器: D:/vscode/mingw64/bin/gcc.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="c-文件"><a href="#c-文件" class="headerlink" title="c++文件"></a>c++文件</h2><p>更改编译器的路径这一个地方</p><p>ctrl+shift+p打开编辑选项：添加配置</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803970.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 174009"></p><p>编译器路径更改为g++.exe</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803971.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 174216"></p><p>打开终端，配置任务，选择c&#x2F;c++：g++.exe生成活动文件，这时候tasks.json文件就会多出一个c++的选项</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;version&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2.0.0&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;tasks&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;cppbuild&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;label&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;C/C++: gcc.exe 生成活动文件&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;D:\\vscode\\mingw64\\bin\\gcc.exe&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;args&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-fdiagnostics-color=always&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-g&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;file&#125;&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-o&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;fileDirname&#125;\\$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;options&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;fileDirname&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;problemMatcher&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$gcc&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;group&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;build&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;detail&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;编译器: D:\\vscode\\mingw64\\bin\\gcc.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;cppbuild&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;label&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;C/C++: g++.exe 生成活动文件&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;D:/vscode/mingw64/bin/g++.exe&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;args&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-fdiagnostics-color=always&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-g&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;file&#125;&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;-o&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;fileDirname&#125;\\$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;options&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;D:/vscode/mingw64/bin&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;problemMatcher&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;$gcc&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;group&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;build&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;detail&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;编译器: D:/vscode/mingw64/bin/g++.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>后面与<a href="###%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6">这一步</a>类似，只是选择g++的选项</p><h2 id="调试"><a href="#调试" class="headerlink" title="调试"></a>调试</h2><p>点击调试后，选择gdb调试器</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803972.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 175313"></p><p>选择你所调试文件对应的编译器</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803973.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 175322"></p><p>生成一个launch.json文件，打开后，选择添加配置</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/rPniu/img@main/img/202405201803974.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-20 175656"></p><p>选择第三个c&#x2F;c++（gdb）启动</p><p>修改选项为</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs swift"><span class="hljs-string">&quot;program&quot;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;$&#123;fileDirname&#125;<span class="hljs-subst">\\</span>$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;miDebuggerPath&quot;</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;D:<span class="hljs-subst">\\</span>vscode<span class="hljs-subst">\\</span>mingw64<span class="hljs-subst">\\</span>bin<span class="hljs-subst">\\</span>gdb.exe&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//你的gdb路径，注意使用两个\\,或者使用一个/</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="ida——python环境"><a href="#ida——python环境" class="headerlink" title="ida——python环境"></a>ida——python环境</h1><p><a href="https://bbs.kanxue.com/thread-279989.htm">原创]ida7使用python问题-IDA Pro插件区-看雪-安全社区|安全招聘|kanxue.com</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
